commit.title: [pcoq] Move entry-specific parts to Pcoq.
commit.message:
[pcoq] Move entry-specific parts to Pcoq.

With this `Pcoq` becomes independent of `Extend`. IMHO this is a step
toward unifying `Pcoq` and `Gramlib` extension mechanisms.

Extension rules are indeed totally specific to `Pcoq` so it makes
sense for that module to control them.
